Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍腐於野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆斷於利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛之人 且赴黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離宮渡口不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀人果真繞到我們前面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如若不然我們取道陸路便沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時 刑部…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正和伊賀人…廝殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的意志 誰都無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得稱讚 刑部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著了你的道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 現在站在這裏的我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會說是幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞刑部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是方便的忍術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最適合夾著尾巴逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想想怎麼殺你們就讓我興奮得發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣五郎閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會為你報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在砍哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧 我的刀不是用來殺甲賀鼠輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若說躲躲藏藏是甲賀的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是伊賀的一貫作風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天正年間的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴我你們已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指哪件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在織田出兵伊賀的前後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍谷先代的屍骸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在村外被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你們的陰謀詭計嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是屬實你當如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑部 因為你躲躲藏藏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害死了無辜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是罪孽深重的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀人居然指責我罪孽深淺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少讓人笑掉大牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒忘記你們的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對忘不了那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼猶豫不決 刑部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為背後偷襲很卑鄙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:09:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是 憐憫敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這個弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有一天會害你送命的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者不需要憐憫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去 就捨棄憐憫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親要去鍔隱谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接連不斷的小衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方似乎也忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為彈正大人的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 你以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的修行也還不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀和伊賀 雙方的宿怨\N並非一朝一夕便能化解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 繼續這麼無意義的流血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你一起平靜地生活也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上我們吃久違的山菜沙鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父親回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會采很多很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀鼠輩 設計我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑部…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者不需要憐憫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為初代服部半藏的仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀和伊賀締結不戰之約
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還未來得及替父親報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配我霞刑部一舉一動的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有對你們伊賀的仇恨、怨懟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我 捨棄了憐憫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可以捨棄的憐憫就已經算幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和你的父親沒有見過人間地獄就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快忘記你那張怯懦的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你好好記清楚 可別跟地獄的小鬼搞混了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿命來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑部 你休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞刑部 幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷了音訊的他們恐怕也不會活著了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵我雙方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手上的棋子 四枚對四枚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 最後活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們伊賀一方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:05.30,name,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(828,30)\frz-90}尾張與三河國境 界橋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有覺得像人的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的惡作劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又走了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 將監 十兵衛 丈助 胡夷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無垢的心眼 澄淨的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識與故鄉別無二致的鄰國
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純真的心在時光流逝中相系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此眼中再次映出對方的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同邁出腳步那日的風音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童真爛漫眼眸的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早春萌芽淡然縹緲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Basilisk 甲賀忍法帖

